  "description": "Mathematical Chain showcase: ORACLE's GENDY stochastic synthesis at moderate stochasticity through Quantum Smear at Observation 0.08 — maximum uncollapsedness. This combination makes the GENDY output live in a permanent state of spectral superposition, where each stochastic event exists in multiple delay times simultaneously until you listen closely. Entropy Cooler at Stability 0.48 provides near-neutral spectral shaping. Voronoi minimal. Attractor Drive off (0.0 mix). The result is a delicate, luminous texture that exists between tonal and textural.",
